  "commentary": "Dealers are currently in a PIN regime with spot at 6604.64 sitting just below the GEX flip at 6609, meaning they're long gamma and will sell any rally toward the massive 6610 wall (70.6B) while buying dips toward 6590 (-31.7B negative gamma). The GEX surge event combined with the tight clustering of positive gamma walls from 6605-6620 creates a strong mean-reverting environment that should cap upside momentum. Watch for resistance at 6609-6610 where dealer selling pressure intensifies, and support at 6590 where dealer buying kicks in.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 6590-6610 with dealers capping big moves in either direction.",
